{"tid":2512221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 第一屆許智峯訪問節目改名大賽","createTime":"2021-05-01T13:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T14:20:53.000Z","uid":360820,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7a02e8a91fee733c23b4d4ddb650dc01c2aec0","tid":2512221,"uid":360820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"智峯大師離開英國前<br />\n我哋搵左喺英國嘅手足做訪問<br />\n睇睇預告先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/6Q9ZVZttHYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6Q9ZVZttHYk&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=f299de27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6Q9ZVZttHYk</a></span><br />\n<br />\n訪問左<span class=\"violet\">3班唔同背景</span>，喺英國申請嘅asylum嘅手足<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">有學生、有中年、有有家室</span></span><br />\n每個人都因為同一個原因黎到英國<br />\n但每個人都有唔同嘅故事<br />\n<br />\n有樣好重要嘅事未決定好<br />\n係就個<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">節目名</span></span>呀！<br />\n所以上黎問下各位巴絲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我先：見人見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c35839f4614f0b3aa2dcbc9e65b690709c41cc","tid":2512221,"uid":360820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85322322692e5e1dc630be251d1bedf1d59f424","tid":2512221,"uid":360820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed3554b6545a527d780510710fd991eedd0773d","tid":2512221,"uid":360820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse